  "description": "This traditional Venezuelan dish is a mouthwatering combination of roasted perilla seeds and steamed vegetables, all on a smoky binchotan grill. The perilla seeds, also known as deulkkae, are said to have hangover-curing properties, making this dish a great choice for a post-party meal.",
