  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the binchotan grill to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Brush the grill with vegetable oil to prevent sticking.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the minced garlic, grated ginger, and a pinch of salt.",
    " Spread the perilla seeds evenly over the grill and roast for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the sliced onion, red bell pepper, and zucchini to the grill and continue roasting for another 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Steam the green onions in a separate pot until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "To assemble the dish, place a scoop of the roasted perilla seeds on a plate, top with steamed green onions, and serve hot."
